Are you saying

9
00:01:15,108 --> 00:01:16,843
you're Veronica Park

10
00:01:17,110 --> 00:01:19,712
and this is our first time
to meet each other?

11
00:01:20,113 --> 00:01:20,947
Yes.

12
00:01:21,014 --> 00:01:22,248
Who are you?

13
00:01:22,982 --> 00:01:25,151
