Call the control center
and get the security camera footage.

33
00:02:59,546 --> 00:03:00,713
Oh, right.

34
00:03:02,549 --> 00:03:03,616
That lady.

35
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,862
-Mr. Do.
-What?

36
00:03:17,730 --> 00:03:19,098
It's me, Ms. Jeong.

37
00:03:19,532 --> 00:03:21,134
Where have you been?

38
00:03:21,201 --> 00:03:22,869
I'll tell you later.

39
00:03:23,169 --> 00:03:26,239
Did you see a loud lady standing here?

40
00:03:26,739 --> 00:03:29,275
-Who?
-I just ran into a woman.

41
00:03:29,342 --> 00:03:31,110
Do you know what she told me?

42
00:03:33,046 --> 00:03:35,815
"Nice to meet you. I'm Veronica Park."

43
00:03:37,951 --> 00:03:41,988
I know we're living in a world
full of swindlers these days,

44
00:03:42,055 --> 00:03:43,723
but how could she be so brazen?

45
00:03:44,224 --> 00:03:45,625
She said we just met for the first time.

46
00:03:45,692 --> 00:03:46,793
We met so many times,

47
00:03:46,859 --> 00:03:48,094
and I even kissed...

48
00:03:51,064 --> 00:03:52,131
Anyway.

49
00:03:52,732 --> 00:03:55,068
She was wearing this strange hat
that looks like a curtain.

50
00:03:55,134 --> 00:03:57,770
You should go inside and look for her.
I'll look for her outside.

51
00:03:58,438 --> 00:03:59,539
Wait.

52
00:04:00,106 --> 00:04:01,341
I guess she's already left.

53
00:04:01,407 --> 00:04:03,009
