Then I should at least tell her.

56
00:04:08,581 --> 00:04:09,616
Who?

57
00:04:09,682 --> 00:04:11,985
Who do you think? The real Veronica Park.

58
00:04:12,285 --> 00:04:14,487
Mr. Do, you don't have to do it now.

59
00:04:17,123 --> 00:04:20,059
